Note that previous releases of the @samp{@value{PACKAGE_TARNAME}} package were intended to provide
additional support to GCOM release of LiS and were released primarily in Tar Ball format.  As of
@value{PACKAGE_TARNAME}-0.9.2-1 this is no longer the case.  @value{PACKAGE_TARNAME}-0.9.2-1 and
