Interface (XTI/TLI) definitions for Stream Control Transmission Protocol (SCTP) that are common to
the kernel and user space programs.  Include this file in kernel or user space programs immediately
after including @header{xti.h} or @header{sys/xti.h}.

This header file is normally installed in the @file{/usr/include/strsctp} directory, so remember to
add @samp{-I/usr/include/strsctp} to your compile line.
